Package DAO

Class AppDAO

  • java.lang.Object
    • DAO.AppDAO
  • public class AppDAO
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used to interact with the connected database and all Appointment objects made. This class includes the Create, Read, Update, and Delete actions associated with the database.
